flowchart LR

    A([Open Dev Mode])
    PRE{Prerequisites met?}
    FAIL([Stop: satisfy Org plan, published library, and AI IDE])

    B[Inspect Design]
    AUDIT[Audit Figma components vs code inventory]
    GAP{Any component gaps?}
    CREATE[Create missing code components]

    C[[Init Code Connect]]
    GH[Connect GitHub (project setup once)]
    D{Select Mapping Method}
    E((Use UI Mapping))
    F((Use CLI Mapping))
    H{Storybook Integration?}
    SBV[Source props/variants from story variants]
    PROPS[Validate props and variants against spec]
    I[Map component]
    MORE{More components?}
    K[[Publish batch to MCP]]

    M[Prompt Copilot]
    N[AI Scaffolds Layout]
    SPEC{Scaffold matches spec?}
    P((Refine by Section))
    QA{Passes QA (visual regression + a11y)?}
    PR[PR and team review]
    Q([Finalize Implementation])

    S[/UI and CLI can coexist, but not on the same component/]
    T[/CLI mappings are strings, not executed code/]
    U[/Treat Figma as spec, not final code generator/]

    A --> PRE
    PRE -->|No| FAIL
    PRE -->|Yes| B

    B --> AUDIT
    AUDIT --> GAP
    GAP -->|Yes| CREATE
    GAP -->|No| C
    CREATE --> C

    C --> GH
    GH --> D

    D -->|UI| E
    E --> PROPS

    D -->|CLI| F
    F --> H
    H -->|Yes| SBV
    SBV --> PROPS
    H -->|No| PROPS

    PROPS --> I
    I --> MORE
    MORE -->|Yes| D
    MORE -->|No| K

    K --> M
    M --> N
    N --> SPEC
    SPEC -->|No| M
    SPEC -->|Yes| P

    P --> QA
    QA -->|No| P
    QA -->|Yes| PR
    PR --> Q

    D -->|note| S
    F -->|note| T
    P -->|note| U
